name: Triviafor30RockFans
0:
”Alexa, ask thirty Rockefeller trivia for a fact”
”Alexa, start thirty Rockefeller trivia”
”Alexa, ask thirty Rockefeller trivia to give me a fact”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: thirty rockefeller trivia
des: This skill generates a random fact about "30 Rock" an NBC Universal show. The user will say something along the lines of "Alexa, give me a thirty Rock fact" and Alexa will read aloud a fact inside the written skill. Alexa will output something along the lines of "Here's your thirty rock fact: 'followed by the fact'".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
